---

<Layout title="Fabiano Moura | Excelência Nutricional">

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
       POPUP MODAL — Hero Card
  ════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <div id="hero-modal" class="modal-overlay" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-label="Bem-vindo">
    <div class="modal-card">

      <button id="modal-close" class="modal-close" aria-label="Fechar">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M18 6L6 18M6 6l12 12" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
        </svg>
      </button>

      <!-- 3 imagens: esquerda opacity-10, centro com glow + objetos, direita opacity-10 -->
      <div class="mc-images">
        <div class="mc-side mc-side-left">
          <Image src={fabiano} alt="" loading="eager" class="mc-side-img mc-img-left" />
        </div>

        <div class="mc-center">
          <img src={luz.src} alt="" loading="eager" class="mc-luz animate-glow" aria-hidden="true" />
          <img src={image1.src} alt="Fabiano Moura" loading="eager" class="mc-main-img" />
          <Image src={objectEl} alt="" loading="eager" width={64} class="mc-obj mc-obj-1 animate-pulse2" />
          <Image src={objectEl} alt="" loading="eager" width={48} class="mc-obj mc-obj-2 animate-pulse3" />
        </div>

        <div class="mc-side mc-side-right">
          <Image src={image2} alt="" loading="eager" class="mc-side-img mc-img-right" />
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Logo sobreposta às imagens (igual ao hero.astro: mt-[-5rem]) -->
      <div class="mc-logo-wrap">
        <Image src={logoPrincipal} alt="Fabiano Moura Excelência Nutricional" loading="eager" class="mc-logo" />
      </div>

      <!-- Texto e CTA -->
      <div class="mc-body">
        <h2>Nutrição de alta performance<br/>para resultados reais</h2>
        <p>Ciência aplicada, acompanhamento próximo<br/>e planos 100% individualizados.</p>

        <a
          href="https://api.whatsapp.com/send?phone=5587988674049&text=Ol%C3%A1%2C%20gostaria%20de%20saber%20mais!"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener"
          class="mc-cta group"
        >
          <span>Agendar avaliação</span>
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M12 22C17.5229 22 22 17.5229 22 12C22 6.47715 17.5229 2 12 2C6.47715 2 2 6.47715 2 12C2 17.5229 6.47715 22 12 22Z"
              class="mc-cta-circle" stroke-width="2" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            <path d="M15.5 8.5L8.5 15.5" class="mc-cta-arrow" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            <path d="M9.5 8.5H15.5V14.5"  class="mc-cta-arrow" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </a>

        <p class="mc-slogan">Science in Sports Performance</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <style>
    .modal-overlay {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      z-index: 9999;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 16px;
      background: rgba(0, 8, 24, 0.78);
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      opacity: 0;
      transition: opacity 0.38s ease;
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .modal-overlay.is-open { opacity: 1; pointer-events: auto; }

    .modal-card {
      position: relative;
      max-width: min(100%, 600px);
      background: #081341 url('/assets/bg-hero.jpg') center/cover no-repeat;
      border: 1px solid rgba(228, 214, 148, 0.18);
      border-radius: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 40px 100px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
      overflow: hidden;
      transform: translateY(28px) scale(0.96);
      transition: transform 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1), opacity 0.5s ease;
      opacity: 0;
      padding-bottom: 28px;
    }
    .modal-overlay.is-open .modal-card { transform: translateY(0) scale(1); opacity: 1; }

    /* Botão fechar */
    .modal-close {
      position: absolute;
      top: 12px; right: 12px;
      z-index: 40;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      width: 32px; height: 32px;
      background: rgba(8, 19, 65, 0.6);
      border: 1px solid rgba(228, 214, 148, 0.25);
      border-radius: 50%;
      color: rgba(228, 214, 148, 0.75);
      cursor: pointer;
      backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
      transition: background 0.2s, color 0.2s, transform 0.28s cubic-bezier(0.34,1.56,0.64,1);
    }
    .modal-close:hover { background: rgba(228,214,148,0.15); color: #fffbd0; transform: rotate(90deg); }
    .modal-close svg { width: 14px; height: 14px; }

    /* Área de imagens */
    .mc-images {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-end;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 48px;
      position: relative;
    }

    .mc-side { width: clamp(200px, 40%, 400px); flex-shrink: 0; z-index: 10; }
    .mc-side-left  { margin-right: -60px; width: clamp(220px, 30%, 300px); }
    .mc-side-right { margin-left:  -80px; width: clamp(250px, 30%, 300px); }

    .mc-side-img {
      width: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      object-position: center top;
      opacity: 0.1;
      transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
    }
    
    .mc-img-left {
      max-height: 280px;
    }
    
    .mc-img-right {
      max-height: 250px;
    }
    
    .mc-side-img:hover { opacity: 1; }

    /* Centro com glow e objetos flutuantes */
    .mc-center { position: relative; z-index: 20; flex-shrink: 0; }

    .mc-luz {
      position: absolute;
      left: 2rem; top: 1.5rem;
      width: 220px;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .mc-main-img {
      position: relative; z-index: 20;
      width: 260px;
      transition: transform 0.5s ease;
    }
    .mc-main-img:hover { transform: scale(1.02) translateY(-4px); }

    .mc-obj { position: absolute; z-index: 30; pointer-events: none; }
    .mc-obj-1 { width: 54px; bottom: 24px; left: -46px; }
    .mc-obj-2 { width: 42px; bottom: 16px; right: -42px; transform: rotate(38deg); }

    /* Logo sobreposta */
    .mc-logo-wrap {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-top: -64px;
      position: relative; z-index: 30;
    }
    .mc-logo { width: 230px; }

    /* Texto */
    .mc-body {
      display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 10px 28px 0;
      gap: 6px;
    }

    .mc-body h2 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 1.35rem; font-weight: 600;
      color: #e4d694;
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      line-height: 1.2;
    }

    .mc-body > p {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
      line-height: 1.4;
    }

    /* CTA — replica exata do Button.astro + global.css .button */
    .mc-cta {
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 8px;
      margin-top: 10px;
      color: #131941;
      font-weight: 600; font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 1.05rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      width: 253px;
      min-width: 120px;
      padding: 8px 16px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #EEE5A6 -10%, #A58D52 20%, #EBDAA2 64%, #FEFFDC 100%);
      border-radius: 0.5rem;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    }
    .mc-cta:hover { transform: scale(1.05); box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(228,214,148,0.5); }
    .mc-cta svg { width: 24px; height: 24px; fill: none; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .mc-cta-circle { stroke: #131941; transition: fill 0.9s ease, stroke 0.9s ease; }
    .mc-cta:hover .mc-cta-circle { fill: #131941; stroke: #131941; }
    .mc-cta-arrow { stroke: #131941; transition: stroke 0.3s ease; }
    .mc-cta:hover .mc-cta-arrow { stroke: #FBF9D3; }

    .mc-slogan {
      margin: 6px 0 0;
      font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 300;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    }
  </style>

  <script>
    const overlay = document.getElementById('hero-modal') as HTMLElement;
    const closeBtn = document.getElementById('modal-close');

    function openModal() { overlay.classList.add('is-open'); document.body.style.overflow = 'hidden'; }
    function closeModal() { overlay.classList.remove('is-open'); document.body.style.overflow = ''; }

    setTimeout(openModal, 400);
    closeBtn?.addEventListener('click', closeModal);
    overlay.addEventListener('click', (e) => { if (e.target === overlay) closeModal(); });
    document.addEventListener('keydown', (e) => { if (e.key === 'Escape') closeModal(); });
  </script>

  <main class="home-page text-text bg-background w-full max-w-full box-border justify-center items-center overflow-hidden">
    <header class="site-header" data-site-header>
      <a href="#inicio" class="brand-link" aria-label="Fabiano Moura Excelência Nutricional">
        <Image src={logoPrincipal} alt="Fabiano Moura Excelência Nutricional" loading="eager" class="brand-logo" />
      </a>

      <nav class="site-nav" aria-label="Navegação principal">
        {menuItems.map((item) => (
          <a href={`#${item.toLowerCase().normalize('NFD').replace(/[\u0300-\u036f]/g, '')}`}>
            {item}
          </a>
        ))}
      </nav>

      <a
        href="/login"
        class="private-access"
      >
        <span>Acesso Exclusivo</span>
        <svg class="private-icon" viewBox="0 0 35 35" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
          <defs>
            <linearGradient id="fire-grad" x1="17.5" y1="35" x2="17.5" y2="0" gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
              <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#ff6a00"/>
              <stop offset="55%" stop-color="#ee2e00"/>
              <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#bf1000"/>
            </linearGradient>
          </defs>
          <path class="fire-path" d="M14.0924 34.4531C11.2527 32.6814 9.84934 28.9929 10.8069 25.8521C11.3022 27.8493 12.7551 29.3473 14.1585 29.8949C13.5806 26.3514 17.1633 23.726 18.7813 21.8898C20.2507 20.2147 20.6304 17.5732 19.0785 15.721C23.1069 18.2819 24.8074 23.8227 22.8758 28.1232C21.9347 30.217 20.2507 32.0693 19.9865 34.3565C21.2743 31.7472 29.6779 30.5392 29.5293 22.8724C29.4468 18.3464 24.081 13.7881 25.9962 9.8581C24.5598 10.7279 23.4866 12.1291 22.7107 14.223C23.7013 6.52399 21.3238 2.41677 17.6751 -0.546875C18.6327 1.17655 18.352 3.4315 17.2458 5.05828C14.6538 8.89169 10.9225 9.55207 11.4673 15.0767C11.5499 15.9465 11.748 16.9773 11.1206 17.6054C10.4437 18.2819 9.07337 18.2658 8.57807 17.3477C8.1323 16.5102 7.98371 15.3827 7.95069 14.4324C6.20063 17.8954 4.71472 22.5824 5.88694 26.2709C7.88465 32.4398 14.0924 34.4531 14.0924 34.4531Z"/>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </header>

    <section id="inicio" class="hero-shell">
      <Image
        src={bgHero}
        alt=""
        loading="eager"
        class="hero-bg"
      />

      <div class="hero-content">
        <div class="hero-copy">
          <p class="hero-kicker">
            Nutrição Clínica à Ciência do Exercício
          </p>

          <h1 class="hero-title">
            Resultados reais,
            <span class="block">construídos com ciência.</span>
          </h1>

          <p class="hero-text">
            O conhecimento aplicado gera poder para transformar vidas. Acompanhamento nutricional individualizado para emagrecer, ganhar massa e elevar sua performance, sem dietas genéricas e sem sofrimento.
          </p>

          <a
            href="https://wa.me/message/UYI2RVF6WWLUD1"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
            class="hero-cta"
          >
            <span>Agendar avaliação</span>
            <svg class="hero-cta-icon cta-arrow" viewBox="0 0 32 32" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
              <circle class="arrow-bg" cx="16" cy="16" r="14" stroke-width="1.5"/>
              <path class="arrow-head" d="M13 11l5 5-5 5" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-visual" id="hero-visual">
          <Image
            src={fabiano}
            alt="Fabiano Moura"
            loading="eager"
            class="fabiano-photo"
            id="fabiano-photo"
          />

          <Image
            src={elemento}
            alt=""
            loading="eager"
            class="hero-element"
            id="hero-element"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="scroll-cue">
        <span>Science in Sports Performance</span>
        <svg class="scroll-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 28" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M6 4l6 6 6-6" stroke="#e4d694" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          <path d="M6 12l6 6 6-6" stroke="#e4d694" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" opacity="0.5"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="especialidades" class="stats-fold">
